Narrowest-Over-Threshold (NOT) Detection of Multiple Change-Points and Change-point-like Features
========================================================
author: Bruno Grillo e Renan Cintra
date: Porto Alegre, abril de 2021.
Séries Temporais (PPGEst - UFRGS)

